dialog.add("Abu Yasser", Abu_Yasser, "Ah, a new face seeking the secrets of the past. Welcome to Thour Cave,\nwhere history whispers from every stone.");
dialog.add("Laila", Girl_Player, "I've heard there's much to learn here. What can you tell me about this place?");
dialog.add("Laila", Girl_Player, "A pigeon? How did it protect the Prophet?");
dialog.add("Abu Yasser", Abu_Yasser, "when the Prophet and his companion were hiding in this very cave,\n a pigeon built its nest at the entrance. Those pursuing them thought the\nuntouched nest meant the cave was empty, thus moving on. ");
dialog.add("Abu Yasser", Abu_Yasser, "Since then, in Makkah, we honor pigeons and spiders, \nnever harming them, as they once protected our Prophet.");
dialog.add("Laila", Girl_Player, "That's an incredible story.");
dialog.add("Laila", Girl_Player, "Now I really want to explore and uncover the secrets of this historic place.");
dialog.add("Abu Yasser", Abu_Yasser, "Can I ask for a favor? I am an old man and need help with this");
dialog.add("Laila", Girl_Player, "What kind of favor?");
dialog.add("Abu Yasser", Abu_Yasser, "My pigeon, the most special of them all, has not returned to me. Can you find her for me?");
dialog.add("Laila", Girl_Player, "Certainly! How will I recognize her?");
dialog.add("Abu Yasser", Abu_Yasser, "She has a unique marking, a white feather in the shape of a crescent\n among her grey feathers. Bring her back, \nand I'll grant you access to the cave");
